  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd2\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbd\u0dd2 \u0db6\u0dd2\u0dbd \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5 \u0daf\u0dd0\u0db8\u0dd3\u0db8\u0da7 \u0d91\u0dbb\u0dd9\u0dc4\u0dd2\u0dc0 \u0dc3\u0da2\u0db6 \u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0 \u0d89\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dba\u0d9a",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sajaba in a protest in front of Parliament against the increase in electricity bills",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The MPs of Samagi Jana Balawega and Samagi Jana Sanandhana engaged in a silent protest in front of Parliament today (29) against the excessive increase in electricity bills.",
        "This protest was held under the leadership of Sajith Premadasa, the leader of Samagi Janabalawega and the leader of the opposition, under the theme, Stop corruption, reduce the electricity bill - the electricity bill is sky high, the whole country is dark.",
        "Members of Parliament of Samagi Janabalaweg Lakshman Kiriella, Tissa Attanayake, Gayantha Karunathila, Mano Ganeshan, Naleen Bandara, Dilip Vedaarachchi, Mujubar Rahman, Chaminda Wijesiri, Hector Appuhami and others were present for this occasion.",
        "The opposition leader had questioned whether the people are being put in trouble by increasing the electricity bills and inviting all-party governments to share the dollars received through the Norochchole coal power plant scam.",
        "The opposition leader said that even though the people are suffering so much, the government is working to drag the country further down the cliff with such scams.",
        "Joining the occasion, the opposition leader further said that neither the party of his relatives nor the media of his relatives can see these things."
      ],
